Comment: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:19.12,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\c&H19272B&\frz9.129\pos(595.889,258.778)}Juumonji\N\N\NSarusuberu\N\N\NChitanda\N\N\NManninbashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!{yo in the bg}{eh, it works}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"People remember their high school days as the high point of their lives."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And people remember the high point of their lives as their high school days."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People say these things because everyone holds fond memories of their time in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I doubt that every high school student would want to remember their school life that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if neither studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor sports,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor socializing are of interest to someone, what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if there are students who prefer to keep a low profile?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I guess that would be a pretty lonely way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you liked making yourself suffer, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making myself suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You turn your back on studying, sports and socializing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real low-profile kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking about yourself before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say I'm turning my back on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saving energy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be bothered doing anything that isn't worth your while.{lit. you're not interested in stuff that you consider troublesome and a waste of time}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your motto is none other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't do anything I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I have to do, I do quickly."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a school with as many clubs as this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone like you who doesn't join a single one is the epitome of keeping a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say that's a lonely way to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then clearly you must want yourself to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't shut up, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a bit late for that? We've been hanging around each other since junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you can head off without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.09,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fnCentury Gothic\b1\blur0.75\pos(646,49)\c&H303B49&}Club entry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.09,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs40\pos(310,215)\frz359.411\blur0.6\c&H354854&}Club name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.09,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs40\frz359.411\blur0.6\c&H1B2E3B&\pos(1081,240)}Club
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.09,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.75\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\c&H263A49&\pos(647,201)}Classics
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A club application form?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joining a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Classics Club, at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would you choose the Classics Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a letter from your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just arrived from India.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Benares, or whatever that place is called.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, poor you. So your sister put you up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have enough members, so the club's at risk of being disbanded.{not k-on at all}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants me to join to keep the club alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't your sister know all kinds of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about aikido holds, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would make it very painful to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you can't say no to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even says here that there's nothing much to do in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's nobody there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could have the clubroom all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be pretty cool having your own private corner of the school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A private corner, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kami High! Fight-o! Fight-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To those living high-energy lives, I salute you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:48.89,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax0.3\fnComfortaa\b1\c&H283B3C&\blur0.7\frz348.437\frx10\fry14\org(810,255)\pos(656,226)}Staff {\fax0.27}Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contrary to popular belief,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't consider saving energy to be objectively the best approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not looking down on energetic people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just stick to my motto:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't do anything I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I have to do, I do quickly."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.54,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55\blur0.5\fnComplete in Him\b1\c&H46636D&\pos(627,296)}Oreki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.05,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\fax0.65\fnComfortaa\b1\c&H253235&\blur0.7\frx16\fry12\org(851,312)\frz335.3\pos(618,304)}Earth {\fax0.6\c&H212C2B&}Sci. Prep. {\fax0.55\c&H1F292C&}room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth floor of the auxiliary building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:28.24,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}Bored, sitting on the windowsill,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:36.38,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}I frown at the wind to hide my awkwardness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:44.47,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(280,0)\blur3\t(0,989,2,\blur0.5)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:49.56,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}I nod uncertainly as I shape
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:55.27,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,the future in my hands feeling mighty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:05:00.44,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}I feel that the wind is bringing change
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:05.53,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's your fault for calling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:12.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}The cloudy sky tells a tale of what's to come
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:21.13,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)}Spread our wings with more courage than ever before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:25.72,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and dark are still vague in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:32.01,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,but still we want to know the reason behind kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:36.56,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,No one so far has ever reached
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.40,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,the shining distance far beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:48.03,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,350)}Let's get there before the past takes it all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:59.29,ep title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1482,473)\blur2\pos(926,557)\clip(586,554,603,599)\t(0,1482,\clip(586,554,1280,599)\t(4485,5000,\clip(1280,554,1280,599)}The esteemed Classics Club has been restored
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the Classics Club, right, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda Eru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, doesn't ring a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Oreki Houtarou from 1-B, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in 1-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}1-A? Could it have been for electives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we take Music together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We only had one class together so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has one hell of a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you doing here, Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined the Classics Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined the Classics Club...{echoes}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You joined the club...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was due to... personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if there's already someone in the club, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rejoice, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The club lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't forget to lock up afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lock up afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the key, how could I have unlocked the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, how the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door wasn't locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when I got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the door was locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I gu—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I was locked in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You locked it from the inside, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had the key! Who else could have locked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you haven't introduced me to your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry. I didn't mean to eavesdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just that, from the ground I caught the miraculous sight of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Houtarou talking with a girl in an empty classroom lit by the setting sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I couldn't help but be intrigued!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to intrude on your tryst, but I didn't know—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. He's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Jokes must be improvised, or they're just common lies."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki, who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Fukube Satoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A would-be man of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would-be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great! Nice introduction, Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chitanda Eru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda? You mean you're {\i1}the{\i0} Chitanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Houtarou, have you never heard of the Chitandas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are quite a few old families in Kamiyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the "exponential four" are really famous.
