Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first character in each of their names is an exponent of ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so people call them the "exponential four" families.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if we're famous or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never heard anyone say that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it up, didn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like suggesting things like that every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they really were exponential!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't encourage him, or you'll never get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the Chitandas' eldest daughter is well known to be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a shining young beauty with top-notch grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember seeing her name a bunch of times on the prefectural honor roll for junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal. I just happen to have a knack for exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to embarrass you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I heard the story. It's quite intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About how Chitanda ended up being locked inside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.34,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,62)\blur0.5\fs100\fnOneDirection\c&H868686&\t(2566,2732,\c&H548CB0&)\pos(637,15)}Door {\alpha&HFF&\t(2524,2858,\alpha&H00&)}Open
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went inside, the door was unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Oreki said that when he came by later,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.76,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(111,0)\blur0.5\fs100\fnOneDirection\c&H868686&\t(2566,2732,\c&HCEB795&)\pos(659,15)}Door {\alpha&HFF&\t(2524,2858,\alpha&H00&)}Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the door had been locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:16.80,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs100\fnOneDirection\c&HE9F5F4&\pos(659,15)}Door Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.01,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs100\fnOneDirection\c&HE9F5F4&\t(\c&H7FA5C4&)\move(659,15,580,-55,25,150)}Door Open
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.01,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs100\fnOneDirection\c&HE9F5F4&\t(0,223,\c&HCEB694&\3c&HD6E7BF&\bord2)\move(645,4,762,91,25,191)}Door Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.38,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs100\fnOneDirection\c&HCEB694&\3c&HD6E7BF&\bord2\move(762,91,778,107,23,357)}Door Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you have just forgotten that you locked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. The doors in Kami High can only be locked with a key, even from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't have locked it from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your collection of useless knowledge is impressive as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call it a database, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, it must have just been locked by mistake somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop thinking about it. Why was I locked inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I wasn't, how could I have entered the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was a mistake, who made it and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just consider it for a moment, Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's mull over this for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda, wait a moment please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a database, so I can't draw conclusions,{this is his catchphrase}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Houtarou is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he starts thinking, he'll reach a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you enter the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About three minutes before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the floor's been making this clattering sound for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can! Just listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hearing's pretty good, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you figured something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the same thing's happening on the floor below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Chitanda entered the room while he was working,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was unlucky enough to get locked inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the key that's available for student use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also a master key,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not available to students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you figured it was someone who works here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty sharp to have realized that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I don't get is how you couldn't hear the door being locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, as for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking at that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Ages older than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, we're not quite finished with the formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What formalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be the Classics Club from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about it, Fukube? Will you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good! Today was pretty cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already in the Handicraft Club and Student Council, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no problem! I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already filled out your application, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Houtarou, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. We should decide who's going to be the club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Houtarou's no good, that much I'm certain about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you happy, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He looked pretty determined before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The esteemed Classics Club has been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with it end my quiet, energy-saving days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You totally misjudged him then, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I shouldn't give up on them just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The thing is that he's this eco-friendly, extreme energy-saving lazy kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to give up that peace. I'll put all I have into living the low-energy lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But he's a pretty sharp thinker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this girl.
