Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.86,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.7\fs25\fnSansation\c&H000000&\pos(287,161)}When all of nature is aglow with the radiance of spring,\N a single bud may blossom into countless flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.86,ep title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\fad(777,0)\blur5\c&H000000&\b1\t(0,400,\blur1)\pos(636,48)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, after classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a first-year girl went to the fourth floor of the auxiliary building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Moonlight Sonata's delicate beauty reached her ears from the music room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The setting sun bathed her in red light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its beautiful tone—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I object.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday it rained, so the sun set behind the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain was drumming gracefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness of dusk was closing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the impression that then clung onto her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the delicate noise of the rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overdoing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As she entered the music room, the melody she had followed died abruptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lid of the piano was open, but no pianist was to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The curtains were closed, and the room was dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she saw her.
